671c32ad28735","tid":266293,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太少</blockquote><br />\n求挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日2.5L</blockquote><br />\n堅定流呀<br />\n有圖有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀書真係一日一支<br />\n但嗰期個人好攰"},{"pid":"8b99e9a1d6767852059821eefab9d19600e687b0","tid":266293,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"試過，4個鐘內六罐"},{"pid":"85b4ac7fa31bc10518c1f57d94137261a4879173","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日都飲咗好撚多水<br />\n喺室內環境工作<br />\n呢啲天氣真係好乞人憎</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線，我冬天都可以沖凍水涼，一到夏天真係想跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82e680d9865b6f3511d872e36182a830d13e3af","tid":266293,"uid":15802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定有糖尿<br />\n戒啦</blockquote><br />\n冬天唔會，夏天真係頂唔緊，特別係我真係超怕熱，個人勁易出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以飲凍水啫</blockquote><br />\n係囉，你可以飲其他寶礦力之類架，點解一定要可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f33d471a4317d18b318f1e1ed27b2e1a31b036","tid":266293,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"飲可樂唔係越飲越口渴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffee6cca31accf9f6c29c9177e650dd76099c8ec","tid":266293,"uid":22440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"屋企對上兩代都有糖尿病<br />\n自己一直都可樂成癮<br />\n一日兩三罐咁<br />\n不過日日都有做運動 我都好驚"},{"pid":"891e9de33ca70c22d0b9d646d985abcd26870ac3","tid":266293,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"【經濟日報專訊】香港人飲汽水由小飲到大，解渴背後卻暗藏病魔。有港男日飲6至7罐，至30多歲已患糖尿病，更併發腎衰竭，未夠40歲已要洗腎，換腎後又出現排斥，結果又要再等換腎。<br />\n本港「腎科之父」唐國隆表示，糖尿病年輕化，近年更已成為腎衰竭主要病因，佔新症46%，腎衰竭患者勢增。<br />\n47歲的李志平，自小喜歡飲汽水，成年後做運輸司機，排汗大，日飲6至7罐汽水解渴，30多歲時已患有糖尿病，後因病情嚴重，更要轉打胰島素針，並併發腎衰竭，9年前開始進行俗稱「洗肚」的腹膜透析，3年前獲捐贈換腎。"},{"pid":"62b07e68de6affc5827689afad22e54398f390bd","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定有糖尿<br />\n戒啦</blockquote><br />\n冬天唔會，夏天真係頂唔緊，特別係我真係超怕熱，個人勁易出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以飲凍水啫</blockquote><br />\n小學已經慣左飲凍水，之後連凍水都覺得悶，近呢幾年直頭除左屋企真係冇凍野啱飲先搵凍水濕下咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b7af84796ae30663121246222dc53769bc3b87","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>太少</blockquote><br />\n求挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日2.5L</blockquote><br />\n堅定流呀<br />\n有圖有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀書真係一日一支<br />\n但嗰期個人好攰</blockquote><br />\n咁我又唔覺攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪因為個人係啦啦吸收左咁多糖，但係夏天又燒能量燒得慢變到冇曬糖，所以覺攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef884c6fbdf9a398f45f420d007fe64881779d36","tid":266293,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"飲水咪算囉 <br />\n<br />\n利申 飲開啤酒"},{"pid":"39635359f5d2ba153c6fcfb45025b846d0c59170","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定有糖尿<br />\n戒啦</blockquote><br />\n冬天唔會，夏天真係頂唔緊，特別係我真係超怕熱，個人勁易出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以飲凍水啫</blockquote><br />\n係囉，你可以飲其他寶礦力之類架，點解一定要可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個字<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Gur！！！</span></span><br />\n我敢食包單，一個人係好熱嘅情況下，冇野爽得過飲又gur又凍嘅甜野，可樂直頭係最佳選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e852bb88ef57f717af5b08b794fb84b1a886725","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲可樂唔係越飲越口渴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b47a87b694bcc57ad85b5389a14833b6bddc6f","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企對上兩代都有糖尿病<br />\n自己一直都可樂成癮<br />\n一日兩三罐咁<br />\n不過日日都有做運動 我都好驚</blockquote><br />\n我都驚，我以前都做開運動幾大隻下，但糖尿好似唔關運動事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> over左就係over,左，屋企有開就更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45817415be7db515391dd5cdc4ce7694dda10ed1","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【經濟日報專訊】香港人飲汽水由小飲到大，解渴背後卻暗藏病魔。有港男日飲6至7罐，至30多歲已患糖尿病，更併發腎衰竭，未夠40歲已要洗腎，換腎後又出現排斥，結果又要再等換腎。<br />\n本港「腎科之父」唐國隆表示，糖尿病年輕化，近年更已成為腎衰竭主要病因，佔新症46%，腎衰竭患者勢增。<br />\n47歲的李志平，自小喜歡飲汽水，成年後做運輸司機，排汗大，日飲6至7罐汽水解渴，30多歲時已患有糖尿病，後因病情嚴重，更要轉打胰島素針，並併發腎衰竭，9年前開始進行俗稱「洗肚」的腹膜透析，3年前獲捐贈換腎。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366d4c1107d06de810939e915c7f6cb2360923b3","tid":266293,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心糖尿阿</blockquote><br />\n甜野同糖尿好似冇乜關系喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2340596c335d0eea7b674ec71556361621383232","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲水咪算囉 <br />\n<br />\n利申 飲開啤酒</blockquote><br />\n個人酒量OK,但係體格唔啱飲，所以都係揀可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8adf904b1ffb2352bf573b890e876219f14662d","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockq