lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17601af3717e5a1e524a3544b0edd889b99d81ef","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煮一大壺平既熟普洱 雪凍飲仲正啦<br />\n茶又有助減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽過唔少人好鍾意飲津路，但飲過真係冇咩興趣<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時都鍾意飲茶<br />\n<br />\n但多數都係去茶樓先入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b8f782415586853918f05af12ab1e54b915783","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲有汽嘅水啦，無糖又Gur 得</blockquote><br />\n試過，冇左隻甜味都差好遠，冇咁滿足<br />\n<br />\n同埋梳打水屈人寺同玉泉飲落都怪怪地<br />\n<br />\n以前都迷過好耐Perrier,但係後尾d人話長飲會生腎石就斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5a79fc1d2a86fca02b6a0a0e747b8efdc00112","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可樂殺精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你日日9坐都殺精啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你唔好坐lor 只好企牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係叫你呢世都唔飲可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好日日飲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反正做乜都殺精 點解唔日日飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢方面我唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n射極都有，幫手殺咁d未嘗唔係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c7d0431eefbe153032c38025942ee8a2068f92","tid":266293,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【經濟日報專訊】香港人飲汽水由小飲到大，解渴背後卻暗藏病魔。有港男日飲6至7罐，至30多歲已患糖尿病，更併發腎衰竭，未夠40歲已要洗腎，換腎後又出現排斥，結果又要再等換腎。<br />\n本港「腎科之父」唐國隆表示，糖尿病年輕化，近年更已成為腎衰竭主要病因，佔新症46%，腎衰竭患者勢增。<br />\n47歲的李志平，自小喜歡飲汽水，成年後做運輸司機，排汗大，日飲6至7罐汽水解渴，30多歲時已患有糖尿病，後因病情嚴重，更要轉打胰島素針，並併發腎衰竭，9年前開始進行俗稱「洗肚」的腹膜透析，3年前獲捐贈換腎。</blockquote><br />\n咁睇唔開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c4d7d78c06c864b35887839c483c2079748d98","tid":266293,"uid":64026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"以前做廚房成日都飲，真係熱到仆街無命賠，一日差唔多3至4罐，係唯獨可樂先可以降溫，諗住出咁多汗咁辛苦應該都無事，但係自己本身都肥，老竇老母都有糖尿之後就戒左飲甜野"},{"pid":"7108c19cf249735a68c93ea38cd491db9d5da5e3","tid":266293,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"唔敢飲太多了 <br />\n飲一罐已經要十分鐘去次廁所"},{"pid":"1dfae55d5093bfd84fd98f20c6fe1a0c262cfd36","tid":266293,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"如果出汗好勁好勁2-3罐會唔會都ok"},{"pid":"8de098705cab548eba66ed427d8286e3d6b1bd34","tid":266293,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果出汗好勁好勁2-3罐會唔會都ok</blockquote><br />\n當我無講過<br />\n排到鹽份排唔到糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飲水算"},{"pid":"892d4132ae276c1e2b2b3a22a61183a0fd046269","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔敢飲太多了 <br />\n飲一罐已經要十分鐘去次廁所</blockquote><br />\n似係本身take左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4068441336be68108a54d8559a5f604607751531","tid":266293,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果出汗好勁好勁2-3罐會唔會都ok</blockquote><br />\n當我無講過<br />\n排到鹽份排唔到糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飲水算</blockquote><br />\n如果排到的話，以我身體體質，我每日應該可以坐住飲3罐都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ed18e5a46500c2bc6f3b9d6e50bfbf320d2ba8","tid":266293,"uid":5181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:07:43.000Z","msg":"可樂真係毒品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日限自己最多一罐"},{"pid":"fdaa890bc836ee6adbad90b5dc93f3ac51b232ec","tid":266293,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>【經濟日報專訊】香港人飲汽水由小飲到大，解渴背後卻暗藏病魔。有港男日飲6至7罐，至30多歲已患糖尿病，更併發腎衰竭，未夠40歲已要洗腎，換腎後又出現排斥，結果又要再等換腎。<br />\n本港「腎科之父」唐國隆表示，糖尿病年輕化，近年更已成為腎衰竭主要病因，佔新症46%，腎衰竭患者勢增。<br />\n47歲的李志平，自小喜歡飲汽水，成年後做運輸司機，排汗大，日飲6至7罐汽水解渴，30多歲時已患有糖尿病，後因病情嚴重，更要轉打胰島素針，並併發腎衰竭，9年前開始進行俗稱「洗肚」的腹膜透析，3年前獲捐贈換腎。</blockquote><br />\n咁睇唔開呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母6罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5675e34ae3357c094fb37ad2bf12b8c7078b4f","tid":266293,"uid":84518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"一日一罐我都覺得好撚離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d5e89d243a406c3fdae28631e1fade09a1d62b","tid":266293,"uid":116155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}